At the age of 24, Herfort left his native Germany aboard the SS Donau, arriving at the port of New York City on August 5, 1876.

At the age of 69, Philip Herfort died on March 24, 1921, in Brooklyn, New York, and is buried in Green-Wood Cemetery.
